description: THERE IS NO "N" IN "RHYTHM" COME ON NOW. FIXED SPELLING OF "RHYTHM". Used 3 note power chords instead of 2. Not quite sure how you can hammer-on from an open to a closed hi-hat O_o so I got rid of that. Fixed notation in all tracks (which was particularly ugly at the end) to make the tab readable and aesthetically pleasing to the eye.
title: Bite To Break Skin
